            <br>
            
Welcome to the Hampton Inn Brookhaven hotel, one of Long Island, New 
            York's best hotels, provides lodging accommodations a short distance 
            from Fire Island Beaches and Long Island's Wine Country. Also, The 
            Hamptons, seasonal homes of the &quot;rich and famous&quot; with quaint 
            shops and restaurants. You are not far from Suffolk Community College, 
            Southhampton College, St. Joseph's College or State University at 
            Stony Brook. Our exceptional Breakfast Bar, is open daily from 6 am 
            to 10 am. We guarantee our guests high-quality accommodations, friendly 
            and efficient service, and clean, comfortable surroundings. The spacious 
            Great Room in which breakfast is served offers a 42&quot; flat screen 
            TV and a wonderful fireplace. Hampton Inn Long Island, Brookhaven 
            offers something unique in the hospitality industry...our 100% Satisfaction 
            Guarantee!
 
            
<ul>
<li>Complimentary Deluxe Continental Breakfast 
<li>100% Satisfaction Guaranteed 
